434
00:15:58,180 --> 00:15:59,140
Look at Mr. Jing

435
00:15:59,700 --> 00:16:00,340
and Mr. Sheng.

436
00:16:00,900 --> 00:16:02,460
They're from an investment firm.

437
00:16:02,660 --> 00:16:05,460
