443
00:16:14,500 --> 00:16:15,380
Back then,

444
00:16:15,580 --> 00:16:17,780
when your mother chose capital,

445
00:16:18,060 --> 00:16:19,940
she abandoned cultural inheritance.

446
00:16:20,460 --> 00:16:21,620
