455
00:16:41,980 --> 00:16:42,740
How could this work?

456
00:16:43,780 --> 00:16:44,300
Unacceptable.

457
00:16:44,300 --> 00:16:44,940
Massive funds involved!

458
00:16:45,100 --> 00:16:45,700
Xue,

459
00:16:46,820 --> 00:16:47,620
