480
00:17:18,100 --> 00:17:20,980
Head of Huasheng Group in Greater China,

481
00:17:21,300 --> 00:17:21,860
Ellie.

482
00:17:31,700 --> 00:17:32,340
Qiao Zhi,

483
00:17:32,500 --> 00:17:33,260
