I won't move.

518
00:18:46,220 --> 00:18:47,180
Let me tell you.

519
00:18:48,420 --> 00:18:49,420
I won't move.

520
00:18:50,300 --> 00:18:50,980
I refuse.

521
00:18:51,660 --> 00:18:53,100
I want to constantly remind myself

522
00:18:53,340 --> 00:18:54,580
