573
00:21:32,220 --> 00:21:32,740
I see.

574
00:21:46,380 --> 00:21:47,020
Losers.

575
00:21:47,380 --> 00:21:48,260
You imbeciles!

576
00:21:50,420 --> 00:21:51,340
Disgraceful!

577
00:21:52,020 --> 00:21:53,380
Sorry, Master.

578
00:21:53,780 --> 00:21:55,660
