618
00:23:50,780 --> 00:23:51,220
What's the matter?

619
00:23:51,500 --> 00:23:53,140
Baiwei Group wants your restaurant.

620
00:23:53,820 --> 00:23:54,420
Name your price.

621
00:23:57,060 --> 00:23:58,860
I've just got it reopened,

622
00:23:59,180 --> 00:24:00,380
