808
00:30:19,620 --> 00:30:20,260
Look at him.

809
00:30:20,340 --> 00:30:21,620
I'll get changed.

810
00:30:21,620 --> 00:30:22,340
Just give me a minute!

811
00:30:23,100 --> 00:30:23,940
Please be careful.

812
00:30:32,860 --> 00:30:33,660
Mr. Xu,

813
00:30:34,180 --> 00:30:34,980
is it

814
00:30:35,180 --> 00:30:35,900
